C++17 + POCO + nginx + redis demo

--------------------------------------
Useful redis command

Test redi
$redis-cli ping

$redis-cli
>SET mykey hello
>GET mykey

exit from redi cli
    $exit or ctrl+c

To see persitent data dir
    redis-cli CONFIG GET dir
remove persistent data file
    sudo rm /var/lib/valkey/dump.rdb
    sudo systemctl restart redis

after conf update 
    sudo nano /etc/valkey/valkey.conf
restart
    sudo systemctl restart redis
----------------------------------------
sudo nano /etc/valkey/valkey.conf

##### redis conf file setting ########
bind 127.0.0.1
port 6379
#no data persistent
save ""
appendonly no

#data persitent
#appendonly yes
#appendfsync everysec
#save 60 1000
